{"word":"abrazar","level":"A1","en":"to hug","ru":"обнимать","de":"umarmen","tr":"sarılmak","examples":[{"es_ar":"Abrazá a tu abuela que hace mucho no la ves.","en":"Hug your grandma, you haven't seen her in a long time.","ru":"Обними бабушку, ты её давно не видел.","de":"Umarm deine Oma, du hast sie lange nicht gesehen.","tr":"Büyükanneni kucakla, uzun zamandır görmedin."},{"es_ar":"Nos abrazamos fuerte en la despedida.","en":"We hugged tightly at the farewell.","ru":"Мы крепко обнялись на прощание.","de":"Wir umarmten uns fest zum Abschied.","tr":"Vedalaşırken sıkıca sarıldık."}]},
{"word":"besar","level":"A1","en":"to kiss","ru":"целовать","de":"küssen","tr":"öpmek","examples":[{"es_ar":"Besá a los chicos de mi parte.","en":"Give the kids a kiss from me.","ru":"Поцелуй детей за меня.","de":"Küss die Kinder von mir.","tr":"Çocukları benim adıma öp."},{"es_ar":"Se besaron por primera vez en la plaza.","en":"They kissed for the first time in the square.","ru":"Они впервые поцеловались на площади.","de":"Sie küssten sich zum ersten Mal auf dem Platz.","tr":"İlk kez meydanda öpüştüler."}]},
{"word":"pasear","level":"A1","en":"to stroll / to walk around","ru":"гулять","de":"spazieren","tr":"gezmek","examples":[{"es_ar":"Paseá al perro un rato, dale.","en":"Walk the dog for a bit, come on.","ru":"Погуляй с собакой немного, давай.","de":"Geh eine Weile mit dem Hund spazieren, los.","tr":"Köpeği biraz gezdir, hadi."},{"es_ar":"Paseamos por el parque toda la tarde.","en":"We strolled through the park all afternoon.","ru":"Мы гуляли по парку весь день.","de":"Wir spazierten den ganzen Nachmittag durch den Park.","tr":"Bütün öğleden sonra parkta gezdik."}]},
{"word":"faltar","level":"A2","en":"to be missing / to be lacking","ru":"не хватать","de":"fehlen","tr":"eksik olmak","examples":[{"es_ar":"Falta poco para llegar, aguantá.","en":"We're almost there, hang on.","ru":"Осталось немного до прибытия, потерпи.","de":"Es fehlt nicht mehr viel bis wir da sind, halt durch.","tr":"Varmamıza az kaldı, dayan."},{"es_ar":"Faltó a la reunión sin avisar.","en":"He missed the meeting without letting anyone know.","ru":"Он пропустил встречу, не предупредив.","de":"Er fehlte beim Meeting, ohne Bescheid zu geben.","tr":"Haber vermeden toplantıya gelmedi."}]}
